  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan Tamil youth committed suicide in Mandapam refugee camp",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Sri Lankan Tamil youth committed suicide in the Mandapam refugee camp in Tamil Nadu.",
        "In the year 2006, a woman named Rani went to Tamil Nadu as refugees from Sri Lanka with one son and three daughters and is staying at Mandapam Refugee Rehabilitation Camp.",
        "In this case, 22-year-old Niroshan, the son of a woman named Rani, a Sri Lankan refugee, has been playing games on his cell phone with his friends for the past few days without going to work.",
        "The enraged Rani then scolded her son to stop playing games and go to work.",
        "After this, the Eelam Tamil youth Niroshan, who was heartbroken due to his mother's reprimand, was lying drunk two days ago.",
        "After that, Niroshan, who was in a coma, was admitted to the hospital by his friends, where he succumbed to his injuries.",
        "Subsequently, the police are engaged in the process of taking the body of the deceased Eelam Tamil youth to the Mandapam Refugee Rehabilitation Camp after conducting an autopsy.",
        "Also, based on the complaint filed by Priya, the sister of the deceased Eelam Tamil youth, the police have registered a case and are investigating.",
        "The people of the area are deeply saddened by the young man who took the tragic decision after his mother reprimanded him for playing games on his cell phone instead of going to work."
      ],
